## 0628 Notes

**Training for markdown using**
- Shortcuts ctrl+shift+M preview
- Purchase books about HTML
  + Get started with thin books


**Training for info searching on websites**
- Use the keyboard up and down, page up and down instead of the mouse to increase the speed of retrieval
- Do not use the mouse to click the maximize and minimize buttons, click on the upper blank part of the window

- Procedures list in README.md (e.g.)

- [Entry for searching "Abcream"](http://app1.nmpa.gov.cn/data_nmpa/face3/dir.html)
  + http://app1.nmpa.gov.cn/data_nmpa/face3/base.jsp?tableId=25&tableName=TABLE25&title=%B9%FA%B2%FA%D2%A9%C6%B7&bcId=152904713761213296322795806604

- Familiar with markdown syntax（too slow）
- Shortcuts command+tab switch applications rapidly
- Use cascade windows to view the open files（applications） on the desktop completely
- Open terminal in folder Directory command+B


**How to use Excel**
- Never merge the cell

- Excel number formats
  + Numeric align right
  + (') for text  align left (无需调整)
  + date & time
- Excel formulas
  + COUNTIF is an Excel function to count cells in a range that meet a single condition.
  + CHISQ chi-square
