## 0629 Notes

**Training for Zettlr using**
- Pay attention to the file extension when saving
- Only use Zettlr for making md. file
- Tips for using Zettlr
  + When searching in PubMed, select all the search results, copy and paste them into Zettlr, and generate the md. format of the URL link of the articles
  + 折纸箭头图标 Export files in other formats.
  + 眼睛图标 Toggle readability mode
  + Explore other skills by myself

**Training for searching on PubMed**
- keywords 检索时如检索不到商品名，检索英文名中的关键词
  + IL-8，Clinical trial，Phase 3 or 4
  + No Chinese articles


**Other keypoints**
